### System admin login (ROOT / SUPERADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "root@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### System admin login - wrong password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "root@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Club member login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/clubs/fc-stockholm/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Club member login - club does not exist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/clubs/unknown/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}